{"tid":91571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"首日市况佳　商戶疑售冒牌公仔 維園年宵停電 熟食檔叫苦","createTime":"2017-01-23T03:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T04:05:18.000Z","uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d47858a8314484e1f96423048ed2eadb0c4e373a","tid":91571,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T03:12:13.000Z","msg":"有攤位擺出大量寵物小精靈公仔，售價介乎200至300元不等，記者發現該批公仔沒有任何標籤，例如百變怪造型的比卡超及傻鴨的外形和比例，並不如正版公仔般對稱，檔員表示該攤位的公仔均由內地廠房訂造，但未有正面回應是否正版。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20170123/s00046/c99faca098d1dab9a259354448fda9e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20170123%2Fs00046%2Fc99faca098d1dab9a259354448fda9e2.jpg&h=9a4248a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另有大學生售賣A5尺寸的水樽，其外形及設計與澳洲品牌的「A5 memobottle」相似。攤位成員之一的林小姐解釋，團隊是基於內地廠房提供的水樽樣辦，印上自行構思的字句，認為水樽屬於二次創作。林續指新年「希望大家開開心心」，對於是否侵權「沒有想想太多」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20170123/s00046/c99f96a7a891850553ac3e62bf4800a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20170123%2Fs00046%2Fc99f96a7a891850553ac3e62bf4800a0.jpg&h=0cffe8c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nfrom 明報<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170123/s00002/1485108522122#sthash.EtFwRQt8.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170123%2Fs00002%2F1485108522122%23sthash.EtFwRQt8.dpuf&d=v2qLAQ%2BorjSrdUSo6SPqx5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=b4d90553\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170123%2Fs00002%2F1485108522122%23sthash.EtFwRQt8.dpuf&h=b1daef78\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170123/s00002/1485108522122#sthash.EtFwRQt8.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"534e78852ac1cd453cbeae3a28aef6184442af2a","tid":91571,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T03:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃圾"},{"pid":"e3c327bd5761d05bff2f97495403c1aa28165f4b","tid":91571,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T03:15:01.000Z","msg":"成班垃圾發錢寒賣老翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ab635684143c9134a4018bc7ee6c6e64300dfb","tid":91571,"uid":40499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T03:15:50.000Z","msg":"年宵根本賣垃圾"},{"pid":"42ef20598df93769b134bda1985ab8d97604c153","tid":91571,"uid":60229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T03:17:28.000Z","msg":"林小姐就梗係開心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b82ec81919af8df99cfc681dc15e13a821b4cfe9","tid":91571,"uid":30044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T03:19:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">港女： 侵權梗係開心啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"d7ac30357cfa9b45b12db90d32ab305a4909a898","tid":91571,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T03:21:50.000Z","msg":"左面條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cae893a40049964b7142f2abf2a56f032ab1fe4","tid":91571,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T03:47:43.000Z","msg":"A5 memobottle&trade;<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.memobottle.com/collections/shop-all/products/a5-memobottle\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.memobottle.com%2Fcollections%2Fshop-all%2Fproducts%2Fa5-memobottle&d=v2qLAQ%2BorjSrdUSo6SPqx5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=596df509\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.memobottle.com/collections/shop-all/products/a5-memobottle</a>"},{"pid":"f9a189ecfacbece923ed2ce0eb7f8d7c3ec92b87","tid":91571,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike"